		.intro.cf
			%p In addition to providing admission to keynotes, sessions, and other conference events, your purchase also includes your choice of the available excursion and lunch combinations Friday afternoon. Excursions will visit sites throughout Grand Rapids and offer you the chance to see in context how place has shaped the design practices of many impressive organizations. 
